request.description:
This endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve a list of shipments from the specified URL. The response of this request is documented as a JSON schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "shipments": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "estimated_delivery_date": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
          },
          "recipient_name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "recipient_address": {
            "type": "string"
          }
          // ... other properties
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```
